    Modifier and Type Method Description
    double getScoreOf​(BasketballTeam bt)
    Returns the score of a basketball team with the formula:
    Score = Sum[score of all players] / number of players in the team.
    double getScoreOf​(FootballTeam ft)
    Returns the score of a football team with the formula:
    Score = Sum[score of all players] + the lowest score in the team (female football); the highest score in the team (male football).
    double getScoreOf​(HandballTeam ht)
    Returns the score of a football team with the formula:
    Score = Product[score of all players] (female football); Sum[score of all players] (male football).
    double getScoreOf​(Team t)
    Returns the score of the parameter team.
